verbose_text: The constitutive STAT3 activation in nAMD is not caused by the abnormalities of the IL-6R / gp130 receptor or the negative regulator SOCS3 as their expression levels were comparable between nAMD patients and controls.
evidence: STAT3 activation in nAMD is not caused by the abnormalities of the IL-6R/gp130 receptor or the negative regulator SOCS3
